[
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "DropdownMenu, and related set of components, allows to create vertical menus with a nested structure that pops up on hover or click (default is on hover).  "
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "You can use UUI "
      },
      {
        "text": "DropdownMenuButton",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " or your custom component as a menu item. "
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\r"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "With the "
      },
      {
        "text": "DropdownMenuButton",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": ", you can: "
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "unordered-list",
    "children": [
      {
        "data": {},
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "type": "list-item-child",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Render a menu item with an icon in the left or right position ('left' as default)."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "data": {},
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "type": "list-item-child",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Highlight a menu item as selected, passing the "
              },
              {
                "text": "isActive",
                "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
              },
              {
                "text": " prop."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "data": {},
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "type": "list-item-child",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Mark a menu item as checked, passing the "
              },
              {
                "text": "isChecked",
                "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
              },
              {
                "text": " prop.\r"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "With "
      },
      {
        "text": "MenuSplitter",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": ", you can divide menu item groups. "
      },
      {
        "text": "MenuHeader",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " provides a header for a group."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "With "
      },
      {
        "text": "DropdownMenuSwitchButton",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": ", you can render a menu item with a switch. The "
      },
      {
        "text": "isSelected",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " prop is used as the switch value, and the "
      },
      {
        "text": "onValueChange",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " callback prop is used to change the switch value. "
      },
      {
        "text": "DropdownMenuSwitchButton",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " can also receive an icon."
      }
    ]
  }
]